Function Reference/the author msn « WordPress Codex
-----------

Displays the MSN Messenger ID for the author of a post. Prior to
[WordPress 2.0](/Version_2.0 "Version 2.0"), the **MSN Messenger ID**
field was set in the user's profile, but the field is currently not
accessible in the
[Administration](/Administration_Panels "Administration Panels") \>
[Profile](/Administration_Panels#Your_Profile "Administration Panels")
\> [Your Profile](/Your_Profile_SubPanel "Your Profile SubPanel") panel.
This tag must be used within [The Loop](/The_Loop "The Loop").

Replace With
------------

No replacement exists for this template tag, as the field was removed
from the [Profile
panel](/Your_Profile_SubPanel "Your Profile SubPanel").

Usage
-----

`  <?php the_author_msn(); ?> `

Parameters
----------

This tag does not accept any parameters.

Example
-------

    <p>Contact me on MSN: <?php the_author_msn(); ?></p>

Change Log
----------

-   Since: 0.71
-   Deprecated: ?
-   Replace By: none

